<dl id="n12063d"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12063d">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12063d"> 63(d)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Herv&eacute; = bard</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Un loup familier lui tenair compagnie, comme &agrave; l&apos;Apollon des Grecs, &agrave; l&apos;Odin des Scandinaviens et au barde breton Herv&eacute;, patron des po&euml;tes armoricains <br><font color="green">[A familiar wolf kept him company, like the Apollo of the Greeks, the Odin of the Scandinavians and <mark>the Breton bard Herv&eacute;</mark>, patron of the Armorican poets]</font> <small> [TLMM]Th&eacute;odore-Claude Hersart, Vicomte de La Villemarqu&eacute;, <cite a>Myrdhinn, ou l'enchanteur Merlin</cite></a> (1862) 22-23</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
